    • tree

      int[][] tree
      This variable represents an Nx3 array of integers. It contains the info, the position of the left and the right subtree of each element of the Binary Search Tree.

    • avail

      private int avail
      This variable represents an integer which shows the first empty line. It is a pointer of the stack that contains the first avail position.
